\f2\fs30 \cf2 4\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 When the whole nation had finished crossing the Jordan,\'a0\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf3 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Last week we saw them discover success!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Like many of us their quest to turn an \'91If only\'92 into a reality was met with immediate success like so many of our own adventures.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 the\'a0Lord\'a0said to Joshua,\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 2\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub \'93Choose twelve men\'a0from among the people, one from each tribe,\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 3\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub and tell them to take up twelve stones\'a0from the middle of the Jordan,\'a0from right where the priests are standing, and carry them over with you and put them down at the place where you stay tonight.\'94\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God tells Joshua to pause.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Which is the opposite of what many of us want t to do but is one of the keys to their success as a nation\
\pard\pardeftab720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf2 \super 4\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub So Joshua called together the twelve men\'a0he had appointed from the Israelites, one from each tribe,\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 5\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub and said to them, \'93Go over before the ark of the\'a0Lord\'a0your God into the middle of the Jordan.\'a0\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Go back to the place of the miracle\
\pard\pardeftab720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 Each of you is to take up a stone on his shoulder, according to the number of the tribes of the Israelites,\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 6\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub to serve as a sign\'a0among you. In the future, when your children\'a0ask you, \'91What do these stones mean?\'92\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 7\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub tell them that the flow of the Jordan was cut off\'a0before the ark of the covenant of the\'a0Lord. When it crossed the Jordan, the waters of the Jordan were cut off. These stones are to be a memorial\'a0to the people of Israel forever.\'94\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Joshua tells the people who God had told him, I want you to pause long enough to create something unique  and that stands out\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s purpose has a dual meaning\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}For your future \'96 to serve as a sign among you\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}So your kids ask what it is\
\pard\pardeftab720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf2 \super 8\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub So the Israelites did as Joshua commanded them. \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The grabbed the stones and the next part explains in more detail about what happened\
\pard\pardeftab720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf2 \super 19\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub On the tenth day of the first month the people went up from the Jordan and camped at Gilgal\'a0on the eastern border of Jericho.\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 20\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub And Joshua set up at Gilgal the twelve stones\'a0they had taken out of the Jordan.\'a0\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}So they are close to battle line now\'85maybe a mile or two away from the walls of Jericho\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Joshua takes 12 stones and sets them up here.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf2 \super 21\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub He said to the Israelites, \'93In the future when your descendants ask their parents, \'91What do these stones mean?\'92\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 22\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub tell them, \'91Israel crossed the Jordan on dry ground.\'92\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 23\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub For the\'a0Lord\'a0your God dried up the Jordan before you until you had crossed over. The\'a0Lord\'a0your God did to the Jordan what he had done to the Red Sea\'a0when he dried it up before us until we had crossed over.\'a0\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He repeats this incredible point.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}In the future people will ask you about this monument you have created\'85make sure you tell others about it.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf2 \super 24\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub He did this so that all the peoples of the earth might know\'a0that the hand of the\'a0Lord\'a0is powerful\'a0and so that you might always fear the\'a0Lord\'a0your God.\'94\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Here is the point of all of this\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0
\f2\b\fs28 \cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Your successes are there for His witness\
\pard\pardeftab720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f3\b0\fs24 \cf5 Illustration of me struggling at times in my life about why God doesn\'92t just fix the situation\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sb100\sa100\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I\'92ve had to learn that God is more interested in me learning, discovering, and proclaiming who He is than me getting to some destination.  \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0\cf3 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Your successes are there for His witness\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl1\cf3 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}When we forget this we lose all power and authority in our lives\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

